---
title: American Beef Enchiladas with Cheddar Cheese & Creamy Pesto Salad
description: Saddle up for a fiesta on the ranch with this irresistible dish! Enchiladas are long bundles of joy, wrapped up tight with cheese melted over. Discover the saucy beef filling, spiced in our All-American fan-fave seasoning and the creamy pesto salad served on the side is just the thing to finish up this plate of happiness.

*We’ve replaced the garlic aioli in this recipe with creamy pesto dressing due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
